title: Various Artists - Navigatorz Fresh!! Indie Playlist August, 2013
description:
This is a fresh!! new!! Indie Playlist for the month 

of AUGUST 2013!! We are happy that we have more and 

more people downloading our list from month to month. 

Many new songs, some of them great, waiting for you 

to give them a chance.If you like them please buy 

original CDs and support the artists. 
Anyone who is interested in sending your own stuff 

(via links to downloads), we would gladly listen to 

your music and include it in our list or radio show 

if we find it good, so more people would hear 

it...This month as always, artwork is from our 

designer Luubenica. 


Best regards

Navigatorz team

NAVIGATOR, music team producing beats,grooves and 

much more...And an awesome DJ team and a soundsystem 

as well proudly presents:

NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! INDIE PLAYLIST AUGUST 2013

NAVIGATORZ FRESH!! INDIE PLAYLIST contains the team's 

choice when it comes to independent music 

acts,ranging from guitar, electronic acts to so 

called "indietronica" and experimental sounds...

Enjoy!


P.S. You can WATCH our suggestion for best video on 

YOUTUBE.On the chanell of GLE Magazin our video 

playlist 


). 20 FRESH!!NEW!! VIDEOS!! SINGLES every month!!!
